Title attribute is added to the paragraph <p> element. This attribute shows itself when mouse hover on the paragraph, it shows as a tooltip.

```
<html>
<body>

<h2 title="header">The title Attribute</h2>

<p title="it's a tooltip">
Mouse pointer hover on this paragraph, the title attribute as a tooltip will be displayed.
</p>

</body>
</html>
```
